<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.9.6">
<l>vilaṅkalāl kaṭala ṭaittu viḷaṅkiḻai poruṭṭu villāl</l>
<l>ilaṅkaimā nakarkki ṟaiva ṉirupatu puyantu ṇittāṉ</l>
<l>nalaṅkoṇṇāṉ maṟaival lārka ḷottoli yēttak kēṭṭu</l>
<l>malaṅkupāy vayalti ruppēr maruvināṉ vāḻnta vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The way I prospered was by embracing Tiruppēr,</l>
<l rend="indent">where eel frolic in paddy fields,</l>
<l>Listening as experts in the four propitious Vedas praise in chanted tones</l>
<l>The one who, having blocked the sea with boulders</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of a shining [marriage] thread,</l>
<l>Severed, with a bow, the twenty arms of the ruler of  Laṅkā  ’s great city.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
